text: Nanga Entulang is a settlement in the Sri Aman District of Sarawak, Malaysia. It is on the southeast bank of the Batang Lupar river, and includes the eponymous stream Sungai Entulang. Neighbouring settlements include: *Rumah Sandai west *Skra northeast *Setumbin north *Sungai Gran north *Temelan east *Bijat south *Kampong Ilir east *Sri Aman east ==References== Category:Populated places in Sarawak Category:Sarawak geography stubs
